A compact IoT system for real-time weather sensing, cloud data logging, and machine learning-based forecasting using SVR, KNN, Decision Trees, and Ridge Regression.

ğŸš€ Features

Real-time metrics: Temp, Humidity, Pressure, Wind Speed/Direction, Rainfall, UV

Google Cloud Storage data upload (ESP32 Wi-Fi)

Custom weather instruments (3D-printed anemometer, wind vane, rain gauge)

ML forecasting pipeline (Python + scikit-learn)

Web dashboard for remote monitoring

